remarks.para:
If not specified,  will be used. It is therefore recommended that this
property be set in order to differentiate the application data from that created by another runtime deployment. For example,
Path.Combine(Environment.GetFolderPath(Environment.SpecialFolder.LocalApplicationData), "Vendor\MyAppName");

The collection may contain any of the following types of LocalService:
LocalMapService;
LocalFeatureService;
LocalGeoprocessingService.
